Modular build: Do incremental updates of Git-based source directories

Update the source directory when the commit ID in tools/REVISIONS has
changed.  Record which Git commit ID was checked out previously.

In order to make this incremental (without deleting the ".git"
directory when the commit ID in REVISIONS changes) the support for Git
sources has moved from dirtree.py to btarget.py.

